instruments. I'm also a freeform Trombonist that like to process the
Trombone sounds in realtime in a concert situation.=20

I've done a couple of concerts involving livecoding, but I've not yet
shown it to the audience with projectors which always has been my
intention, to show my workingplace and my 'instument' of the musicmaking
side, and give the audience a better understanding of the playing part
of the performance.=20

