> preparing a proposal- (I know your funds are limited, it's just how 
limited
> : ) )  we have some far-flung members, and some very close ones.

Let's stick to the close members and see what we can do with them. Flights
from London, Paris or most other european cities are cheap and reasonable,
the US or other places abroad will be a problem. accomodation can be
arranged. hotel if necessary, but limited. otherwise we have some artist
flats, where we easily can accomodate people. we also server breakfast
there. So far I think of a maximum of 3-4 people.



