hi again,

the venue is Maria am Ostbahnhof, a huge club where we did the last club
transmediale festival also. but this time we will open up an additional
room, not used before. This room is meant more as a cinema. we will have
seats and a huge central screen. but is not a problem to split this up in
two screens or have additional screens. It is of course a question of money,
but I know that you probably will need more than one screen. How many are
needed?

