Date: Mon, 17 Jan 2005 13:19:15 +0100
From: Anke Eckardt <anke
Subject: [livecode] technical riders for club transmediale 05


Dear acts of club transmediale 05,


for the upcoming club transmediale 2005 festival our technicians need=20
very EXACT TECH RIDERS including a



     * Stageplan (drawn)



     * an inputlist wich channels will be used for wich gear



     * wich gear the act will bring and what we have to provide for them




we=92d kindly like to ask u to give us all the lacking
information as soon as possible !
for your evening we plan to have a cinema-situation: that means
people sitting on chairs, looking at one big screen, in front of the=20
screen there will be a stage for the artists and we use a stereo-PA
left as right you will have one top and one subspeacer.

so far...*****
PLEASE ANSWER TO  anke@hiddende
thanks, and all the best from berlin



anke




