Date: Wed, 19 Jan 2005 23:32:12 -0800 (PST)
From: Amy Alexander <amy
Subject: Re: [livecode] technical riders for club transmediale 05 (fwd)


thanks nick! i've assembled this page which hopefully will answer all 
anke's questions. can folks try to take a look and see if i've missed 
anything or if anything needs revision? 

http://toplap.org/?node=TransmedialeTechPlan

in the drawing, i've put 7 performers on stage at a time - 5 on the back 
of the table and 2 on the ends. (this is of course just a stab in the dark 
- in reality it depends how big the table is.) i'd like to be on an end 
again because of the visual components to my performance. so if someone 
else is on the other end, it could balance things out and hopefully this 
helps more of us get on stage at once.

