Date: Thu, 20 Jan 2005 16:14:17 -0800 (PST)
From: Amy Alexander <amy
Subject: Re: [livecode] technical riders for club transmediale 05 (fwd)


i do like blending also, at least most of the time. emphasizes 
the dynamics of coding as the screen is almost always "moving" even 
when one person's screen isn't changing much. and creates interesting 
visual rhythms between the various screens' movements.

i'm thinking having 2 superimposed much of the time might be a bit clearer 
than 3 though. but we could definitely turn at least the switched 
projection to black easily - just not sure how it will work with the other 
2.

