probably what you really want; it's a 1.3GB download.  i don't plan to 
keep it in a publicly accessible directory permanently due to the file 
size, so if you can grab it within the next few days that'd be cool. 

perhaps we should put it on bit torrent if more people want it... 


CL> 	Chris would love to have us over to their bitchin' new concert hall
CL> for a show, by the way. I'm very up for it... is anyone else going be around
CL> in the next several months?
CL> 

i'll be here in san diego (gone for much of december but back in early 
january.) so if others can get over there at a particular time, i probably 
could too. 

