Tech, USA
Mark Ball, Fierce Earth Festival, UK 
Christopher Baugh, School of Drama, Film and Visual Arts, University of
Kent, UK
Johannes Birringer, AlienNation Co. USA, Brunel University, UK, Schmelz,
GER 
