f I chose a tough theme, there would be a break at the start of the set
<br>while I tried to get some basic functions coded- sometimes 5 minutes be=
fore<br>any sound! All the sessions were from scratch live coding, so eithe=
r a<br>forgiving connoisseur audience, a duet partner, or cover material fo=
