From: Andrew Sorensen <andrew
Subject: [livecode] Impromptu 0.97
Date: Thu, 23 Nov 2006 20:56:04 +1000


Impromptu 0.97 has just been released.

The primary additions are:

Audio In
Video In
A bidirectional realtime ObjC-bridge

... along with a host of minor additions, performance enhancements  
and bug fixes.

The Impromptu website also includes a bunch of new tutorials (with  
more on the way) as well as new example code.

http://impromptu.moso.com.au

Enjoy!

Andrew Sorensen


