The 2007 LOSS/TOPLAP thing in Sheffield *will* happen, with a related
gig in London too.  Some funding has been secured.  Perhaps that will be
a good time to recollect our thoughts and/or disband TOPLAP and form
something new :)

We need to collectively decide on a date for the Sheffield event, any
preferences?

