From: Andrew Sorensen <andrew
Subject: [livecode] Impromptu 0.98
Date: Mon, 12 Feb 2007 12:46:04 +1000


Impromptu 0.98 is now available for download from
http://impromptu.moso.com.au/downloads.html

The primary addition for this release is OpenGL support.  Currently  
only a subset of opengl is implemented but this will expand with  
future releases.  Please let me know if your favorite opengl function  
isn't available.

You can find examples, videos, recordings, tutorials etc. on the  
impromptu website.

Cheers,
Andrew.S


