Date: Tue, 06 Mar 2007 11:59:25 +0000
From: Nick Collins <nc272
Subject: [livecode] Hybrid TOPLAP


Dear all,

The new Hybrid Arts category of ArsE Lec below might be a suitable venue 
for a TOPLAP submission? I'm happy to put something together (using Ade's 
existing video for the main DVD)

http://www.aec.at/en/prix/cat_hybrid_art.asp

Would people be happy with this? We have some documentation already, I'd 
throw in copies of related academic papers keeping it up to date and 
suggest how we could put on great exhibition performances and collaborative 
coding sessions as part of their festival?

(it would just be a general entry as TOPLAP, hopefully to get as many of us 
there as possible in the event that they're interested).

best,
Nick




