>> already, I'd throw in copies of related academic papers keeping it
>> up to date and suggest how we could put on great exhibition
>> performances and collaborative coding sessions as part of their
>> festival?
>>
>> (it would just be a general entry as TOPLAP, hopefully to get as
>> many of us there as possible in the event that they're interested).
