Subject: [livecode] april 14th
From: alex <alex
Date: Wed, 11 Apr 2007 21:07:42 +0100



A few days to go for the deadline, here is a clarification I just mailed
to someone, perhaps the call is not completely clear so...

The call was for several related things at once:

1/ call for presentation abstracts
2/ call for paper abstracts for proceedings
3/ call for performance abstracts
4/ call for commission applications

My hope is that everyone who does 1/ will also do a related 2/, but it
is not mandatory, for example someone might want to demo their software
without writing about it.  3/ is also encouraged!  4/ is related to 3/,
if you have an idea for a performance but some money would help to
realise it, please apply for a commission.

A couple of paragraphs abstract is fine, if you can get your idea across
in that.

Not many applications for the commissions as yet.  There's a couple for
=C2=A31000 and a few more for a few hundred, ringfenced by the funding
organisations...

Best wishes,

alex




