Date: Thu, 7 Jun 2007 10:41:46 +0100
From: "Jim Prevett" <jp
Subject: Re: [livecode] Workshops at LOSS Livecode


------=_Part_34567_29502395.1181209306956
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=ISO-8859-1; format=flowed
