h
> accurate numbers. Size wise- it would comfortably seat about 20-25 peop=
le
> and could be pushed to hold more although it would then get very intima=
te!

That sounds good. I'm not sure if we have any idea about numbers yet - it
might be an idea to add a tickbox to the registration to get an estimate =
