On 6/15/07, alex <alex@hiddenorg> wrote:
 >
 > Is this book from 1993 known?
 >
 > http://books.google.com/books? 
id=0drDRT370eoC&pg=PP1&ots=eCnQ4eSwos&dq=small+matter+of 
