From: Andrew Sorensen <andrew
Subject: [livecode] impromptu 0.99 released
Date: Sun, 1 Jul 2007 12:08:30 +1000


Hi Everyone,

Impromptu 0.99 has just been released.  This will be the final major  
release before version 1.0.

The major additions for 0.99 are:
Realtime capture of any graphics or opengl canvas to a quicktime  
movie - with Audio of course :)
Completion of pseudo namespace changes.
A bunch of handy new keyboard shortcuts.
A host of minor feature additions, stability improvements and bug fixes.

http://impromptu.moso.com.au

Cheers,
Andrew.


