which is the sacred ChucKist book of "things that we will have in the =
future if we remain faithful". It's probably our largest book, eclipsing =
even the epic "Things that should be documented" tome.<SPAN =
class=3D"Apple-converted-space">=A0</SPAN><BR></SPAN></BLOCKQUOTE></DIV><B=
R><DIV>He he!</DIV><DIV><BR =
class=3D"khtml-block-placeholder"></DIV><DIV>Fantastic.</DIV><DIV><BR =
class=3D"khtml-block-placeholder"></DIV><DIV>May the SporK (or whatever =
you call it in ChucKian) be with you.</DIV><DIV><BR =
class=3D"khtml-block-placeholder"></DIV><DIV><BR =
class=3D"khtml-block-placeholder"></DIV></BODY></HTML>=

