> language.

"Emacs is written in Lisp, which is the only computer language that is  
beautiful." ? Neal Stephenson, In the Beginning Was the Command Line

It is a beautiful language and very expressive. It's my language of  
choice for artistic projects.

If you can program JavaScript you can program Lisp.  This is a good  
online introduction (also available as a nice hardback book :-) ):

