              Michel Waisvisz</font><br><a href=3D"http://www.crackle.org/"=
>http://www.crackle.org/</a><br><br>He specialises in this.<br><br>&gt;A lo=
t of people tell me that al jazari looks fun because you could make<br>elec=
tronic music on it drunk. I think this is also incredibly important
<br>somehow, but I haven&#39;t thought it through properly yet...<br><br>Th=
is was one of my main design criteria; it has to be playable after a 6pack,=
 in pitch dark while somebody is trying to talk to you. I found that to be =
important criteria after playing some amount of live gigs but if you still =
doubt I will be happy to buy you a few drinks in the name of science!
