Date: Tue, 05 Feb 2008 08:53:26 +0000
From: Nick Collins <nc272
Subject: Re: [livecode] icmc08


always nice to see live coding.

off-ICMC is always curated from amongst the standard ICMC music submissions 
as far as I'm aware. So you just submit a proposal in the usual way.

I guess a counter-ICMC could also be run, but a few live code performances 
have appeared at previous ICMCs now, so there is a precedent of inclusion 
at least in off-ICMC, if not in the midday granular synthesis concert.

best
N



