; territory, partially because of the striking omission of feeding the rand=
omly generated insult-strings to the speech synth. Still, one shouldn&#39;t=
 blow it all on the first round so no harm done there.<br>
<br><br>Keep it real,<br>Kas.<br><br><br>;=AC)

