I got a new prototype working:

  http://doc.gold.ac.uk/~ma503am/alex/poei-hoio-_-topo-_-_/

The recording clips a bit, and isn't in stereo (you should be able to
hear half the mesh in each ear), and google video transcoded it to be
barely readable at all...  You can look at the avi version to at least
fix the last problem though.

Feedback most welcome...





