Hi. I just read about this in a gaming magazine.

http://www.retrodev.co.uk/MiscGames/NakedGame/TheNakedGame.html

It's a flash-remake of Pong, where you can comment out lines of code,
and the game will instantly respond according to your changes.=20

I think this is a perfect way to teach non-programmers about code, and a
great tool for debugging - but you already knew that. :-)

Gasten

