Subject: [livecode] instructions via headphones


Dear all,

I include below a link to a short work by Click that might amuse some of 
you. It's intended for headphone listening only, and you might find it most 
effective if you listen whilst there are other people around; perhaps in an 
office? There are possibly tenuous links to live coding; well, at the very 
least, there are some instructions.

best,
Nick



Click Nilson
Instructions
(around 3 minutes long)

http://www.informatics.sussex.ac.uk/users/nc81/music/CNinstructions.mp3




