Hi all,

I've set up an installation version of Al Jazari in the AlHambra, Granada=
,
Spain. It's part of "Youniverse" which is this year's Seville Biennale,
and runs till January 11th.

It's in the Palace of Charles V, so it finally really is livecoding for
royal drinking parties!

http://www.flickr.com/photos/dave-griffiths/2910548240/
http://www.fundacionbiacs.com/biacs3/index.php
http://www.pawfal.org/al-jazari/

cheers,

dave




