It was just a throw-away comment.

I got a bit excited thinking how you could make music with it, then  
watched the demo videos and found it mostly makes metallic clanging  
noises, and then industrial/musique concrete popped into my mind, and  
then Andrew McKenzie, and then I figured he could just plug this  
application into a sound system and he'd be sorted, then I closed my  
browser window and got on with my work.

Sorry.



