Hi all,

Long long before Mac vs PC, the original flamewar was all about Spectrum
vs Commodore. This is essentially a livecoding contest between Italian
geeks in 1985.

"After some orange juice and biscuits, the competition starts."

http://www.alfonsomartone.itb.it/fztsmo.html

